::Battera::

She smiled and looked down, blushing.  She then looked up into his 
eyes. "Don't worry about the Predacons.  For now, We have the Maximal 
leader willing to go to the talks.  She has agreed to go with  us to 
the embassy."  She smiled and raised her hand and gently touched his 
cheek.  "I missed you too." She said in a soft voice.
